EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
S E N A T E R E S O L U T I O N
EXTENDING THE REPORTING DATE OF THE SPECIAL LEGISLATIVE COMMISSION
TO STUDY THE GOVERNANCE STRUCTURE OF RHODE ISLAND'S PUBLIC
EDUCATION SYSTEM
***
1 This resolution would extend the reporting and expiration dates of the special legislative
2 commission to study the governance structure of Rhode Island’s public education system, from
3 March 1, 2025 to April 1, 2026, and said commission would expire on June 1, 2026.
